Package: api.catalogueoflife.org
Title: Catalogue of Life API Client
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for the Catalogue of Life API. Search for
    taxa by scientific name and retrieve detailed taxonomic information
    including classification hierarchy. Includes LLM context injection via
    col_context().
